⚡️⚡️Future Female x Anthropologie collaboration ⚡️⚡️is live on line and in all UK stores. Privileged to work with @rollinfunky @phyllidaswift & @n4mummy on our recent storytelling shoot with @karolinabarnes & @estilamag The Future Fe+Male stories from these wonderful women coming soon. In the meantime scroll through to see the full collection. 👉🏻👉🏻👉🏻 first photo credit @karolinabarnes Future Female advisory board member. . A massive thanks to @zebedee_management for connecting us with Clara. The work you do is inspirational. 🙌🏻🙌🏻
.
⚡️⚡️Anthropologie is a brand with collaboration in its DNA, a magical place I got lost in when I first visited NYC in 1997. ✨✨When I launched Future Female in 2017 I could not have imagined we would get to collaborate with Anthropologie, 🌈and have a chance to be a tiny part of that magic. 🌈⚡️💥That 20 something ME in NYC is hysterical with excitement because some part of me knew I would arrive at this place in the future to shout about everyday equality! .
.

@mrs.mikky.tee thank you we are very proud ❤️
Love this! Such a fun day with you all ❤️🙌 can't wait to see the t-shirts in store! Thanks @deborah_campbell1 for having me on board!
@rollinfunky you are very welcome and it was our pleasure to have you be part of the shoot. 💕
It was such a lovely morning shooting with you all. Thanks @deborah_campbell1 for having me be part of this positive movement ❤️
@n4mummy thank you Karen, very humbled to be part of this movement 🙌🏻
Such an honour to be part of this! But the huge 🙌🙌👏👏👏 goes to you @deborah_campbell1 for setting up something so amazing. Congratulations X
So exciting to see this now live!! Great to be part of it. 👏😘
Great work Deborah! Congratulations and so well deserved 😍
Woah this is incredible!!! I 💖💖 Anthropologie!! So very impressive go you! 👏🏼👏🏼👏🏼
Beautiful designs! Some I hadn’t seen before. 💜
